#: ../../source/janim/items/effect/mask.rst:2
msgid "mask"
msgstr "mask"

#: janim.items.effect.mask.ShapeMask:1 of
msgid "以 ``shape`` 为轮廓做一个蒙板效果"
msgstr "Create a masking effect using ``shape`` as the outline"

#: janim.items.effect.mask.ShapeMask:3 of
msgid "对于传入的物件，只会显示形状内部的部分"
msgstr "For the passed items, only the parts inside the shape will be shown"

#: ../../source/janim/items/effect/mask.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr "Parameters"

#: janim.items.effect.mask.ShapeMask:5 of
msgid "蒙板图形，若带有后代物件，则将若干后代物件图形作 XOR"
msgstr "Mask shape; if it has descendant items, the descendant shapes are combined using XOR"

#: janim.items.effect.mask.ShapeMask:6 of
msgid "蒙板整体透明度，范围 ``0.0 ~ 1.0``"
msgstr "Overall mask opacity, in the range ``0.0 ~ 1.0``"

#: janim.items.effect.mask.ShapeMask:7 of
msgid "边缘羽化大小，值越大越模糊；数值上体现为羽化部分的两侧的距离"
msgstr ""
"Edge feather size; the larger the value, the blurrier it becomes; numerically, it is reflected as the distance on both "
"sides of the feathered region"

#: janim.items.effect.mask.ShapeMask:8 of
msgid "反转蒙板， ``0.0`` 为正常， ``1.0`` 为完全反转"
msgstr "Invert the mask; ``0.0`` is normal and ``1.0`` is fully inverted"

#: janim.items.effect.mask.ShapeMask:10 of
msgid ""
"text = Text('Hello').show()\n"
"mask = ShapeMask(text, shape=Circle(radius=2), feather=0.2)\n"
"mask.show()"
msgstr ""
"text = Text('Hello').show()\n"
"mask = ShapeMask(text, shape=Circle(radius=2), feather=0.2)\n"
"mask.show()"

#: janim.items.effect.mask.ShapeMask:16 of
msgid "若 ``shape`` 要使用后代物件的并，可参考 :meth:`~.boolean_ops.Union.from_group` ，例如"
msgstr ""
"If you want ``shape`` to use the union of its descendant items, see :meth:`~.boolean_ops.Union.from_group`, for example:"

#: janim.items.effect.mask.ShapeMask:18 of
msgid "ShapeMask(..., shape=boolean_ops.Union.from_group(shape))"
msgstr "ShapeMask(..., shape=boolean_ops.Union.from_group(shape))"

#: janim.items.effect.mask.ShapeMask:22 of
msgid "嵌套蒙板和 :class:`~.FrameEffect` 一样，需要显式嵌套 :class:`~.ShapeMask` 对象："
msgstr "Nested masks, like :class:`~.FrameEffect`, require explicitly nesting :class:`~.ShapeMask` objects:"

#: janim.items.effect.mask.ShapeMask:24 of
msgid ""
"mask1 = ShapeMask(..., shape=shape1).show()\n"
"mask2 = ShapeMask(mask1, shape=shape2).show()"
msgstr ""
"mask1 = ShapeMask(..., shape=shape1).show()\n"
"mask2 = ShapeMask(mask1, shape=shape2).show()"

